      <title>中国禁止风险信托向地方政府融资平台销售理财产品</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/china-bans-risky-trusts-from-selling-wealth-products-for-lgfvs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国政府为遏制日益加剧的金融风险采取了最新举措，要求部分信托公司停止从个人筹集资金来资助地方政府融资平台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-21/china-bans-risky-trusts-from-selling-wealth-products-for-lgfvs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 21 Aug 2024 08:01:52 GMT</pubDate>
